{"type":"message","id":"d5ee76ad","parentId":"817dbeb1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T14:03:45.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The FE calls `/dashboard/stats` which is the BE endpoint. The FE `cbe45c6` fix aligns with BE `ca6c6fe` dashboard stats.\n\nNow let me check the BE's dashboard controller response to make sure the `counts` structure matches what the FE expects.\n\nFrom the BE diff I saw:\n```typescript\ncounts: countsMap,  // { total, tuitionDebt, ...statusKeys }\n```\n\nAnd the FE uses:\n```typescript\nstats?.counts?.total\nstats?.counts?.[k]  // where k comes from Object.keys(stats.counts).filter(...)\n\n\n```\n\nThe two branches are compatible—the `cbe45c6` fix in `feat/database-master` already aligns with the BE's `ca6c6fe` changes. Since the FE has all its changes on `feat/database-master` and the BE has its changes on `feat/notification-migration`, I need to decide the merge strategy. Both branches are derived from `origin/develop`, so I should recommend merging both into develop simultaneously to keep them in sync.\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"d6689ecdc600e09633095a4b09b302388cd16bca1fec45b3977daabfecdb5001"},{"type":"text","text":"Tình hình rõ ràng rồi. Cả hai branch tương thích — `cbe45c6` trên FE đã align với `ca6c6fe` trên BE. Migration Phase 3 cũng đã executed ✅\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Phân tích — Sẵn sàng merge\n\n| Check | Kết quả |\n|---|---|\n| BE `feat/notification-migration` vs `origin/develop` | 37 files, 3166 insertions |\n| FE `feat/database-master` vs `origin/develop` | 38 files, 10813 insertions |\n| FE dashboard API contract aligned | ✅ `cbe45c6` fix đã có trong branch |\n| Notification migration Phase 3 executed | ✅ Verified 2026-04-11 |\n| Referential integrity | ✅ 100% |\n\n**Cả hai branch không conflict nhau — merge vào `develop` an toàn.**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Kế hoạch Merge\n\n```\n1. Merge FE feat/database-master → origin/develop\n2. Merge BE feat/notification-migration → origin/develop\n3. GitLab pipeline trigger → deploy\n4. Smoke test dashboard + notification\n```\n\nLead đồng ý thì Orbis bắt đầu merge ngay?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":148,"output":505,"cacheRead":48036,"cacheWrite":463,"totalTokens":49152,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776002613325,"responseId":"062ad936b7f64ed9fdf21a74a13fc1e4"}}
