{"type":"message","id":"325c9223","parentId":"2e0cc72f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:35:18.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me compile the mandatory tasks:\n\n**DTLX Backend:**\n1. MR !166 - 22 commits ahead of develop, pipeline passed (268), can_be_merged - needs Lead approval to merge\n2. `hotfix/unicode-normalization-nfc` - merged via MR 162, pipeline passed - ✅ Done (wait, pipeline 256/257 shows it merged into production? Let me check)\n3. `hotfix/import-student` - not merged yet - needs review\n4. `fix/build-operability-and-typos` - not merged\n\n\n5. `optimization/conventions` - not merged (pipeline 269 - MR 167, success)\n6. `refactor/split-app-server` - not merged\n7. `refactor/merge-api-common` - not merged\n8. `refactor/antigravity` - not merged\n\nThere's also MR 167 for the conventions branch that I need to track.\n\nLooking at the most recent pipelines, MR 167 passed successfully, but MR 166 is still open and has multiple failed attempts before eventually passing on the 268th try. The unicode normalization hotfix was merged through MRs 161 and 162 on March 19th, while the CI checks on the build-operability fix have been failing consistently.","thinkingSignature":"7b6dbefaf236c9064c012eb6eae35b83f893f42357c69279870ca0b180383d25"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6gl1mh6awm3u_1","name":"gitlab__gitlab_list_merge_requests","arguments":{"project_id":"77055841","state":"opened"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":7124,"output":317,"cacheRead":75279,"cacheWrite":1674,"totalTokens":84394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776069299960,"responseId":"062bddb598ea9af83603b7026d45244b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"abe2ce48","parentId":"325c9223","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:35:21.875Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6gl1mh6awm3u_1","toolName":"gitlab__gitlab_list_merge_requests","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[\n  {\n    \"id\": 467782406,\n    \"iid\": 166,\n    \"project_id\": 77055841,\n    \"title\": \"Refactor(Phase1): Restructure routes into presentation/api layer\",\n    \"description\": \"- Created src/presentation/api/ with v1 route files\\n- Migrated system, education, operation, notification routes\\n- Created auth.route.ts for public routes (auth, guests, devices)\\n- Created v1/index.ts with auth middleware separation\\n- Updated app.ts to import from ./presentation/api\\n- Fixed orphaned student.route.ts payment routes → paymentsController\\n- Removed old src/router.ts and src/routes/\\\"\",\n    \"state\": \"opened\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-27T02:49:45.031Z\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-30T02:14:08.575Z\",\n    \"merged_by\": null,\n    \"merge_user\": null,\n    \"merged_at\": null,\n    \"closed_by\": null,\n    \"closed_at\": null,\n    \"target_branch\": \"refactor/main\",\n    \"source_branch\": \"feature/clean-architecture-migration\",\n    \"user_notes_count\": 0,\n    \"upvotes\": 0,\n    \"downvotes\": 0,\n    \"author\": {\n      \"id\": 29160767,\n      \"username\": \"ninhkhuongpl7\",\n      \"public_email\": null,\n      \"name\": \"khuong ninh\",\n      \"state\": \"active\",\n      \"locked\": false,\n      \"avatar_url\": \"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0272ae77fdbd1dc20257bb15df743e9271352040c8fecc313ab6b4649211a7f8?s=80&d=identicon\",\n      \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ninhkhuongpl7\"\n    },\n    \"assignees\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": 29160767,\n        \"username\": \"ninhkhuongpl7\",\n        \"public_email\": null,\n        \"name\": \"khuong ninh\",\n        \"state\": \"active\",\n        \"locked\": false,\n        \"avatar_url\": \"https://secure.gravatar.c