{"type":"compaction","id":"e8d09bb9","parentId":"c6539812","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:50:23.859Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. **QLHV**: Complete BE/FE branch merge to `develop` — BE MR !6 already created and awaiting Lead approval/merge; FE already merged by Lead.\n2. **DTLX Backend**: Fix 35+ TypeScript build errors in `feature/clean-architecture-migration` branch, then start the server on port 5555.\n3. **DTLX Frontend**: Already running on port 3000 (started manually).\n4. **DTLX API testing**: Module-by-module auth API testing after BE is running.\n5. **System deployment**: Deploy full DTLX system (FE + BE working together).\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Orbis is ONLY allowed to work on ahv-qlhv project (confirmed by Lead Apr 12 13:57).\n- For DTLX work (API testing/deployment), Lead later asked for full system deployment (\"triển khai toàn bộ hệ thống\" / \"làm từng module một\").\n- API testing should be done module-by-module after backend is fixed.\n- Never push or commit code; read-only API testing only.\n- Do NOT spawn TroLy model subagents. Use AHV-Holding-DEV workspace directly.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] QLHV BE `feat/notification-migration` pushed to GitLab\n- [x] QLHV BE MR !6 created: `feat/notification-migration` → `develop` (ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be!6)\n- [x] QLHV FE `feat/database-master` merged into `develop` (done by Lead manually, commit `3259abe`)\n- [x] DTLX FE started: http://localhost:3000 (Vite, port 3000, VITE_API_SERVER=http://localhost:5555, branch `main`)\n- [x] **Root cause identified**: Services return `{ data, meta }` but interfaces declare `docs` field; pagination meta uses `limit`/`page` vs `itemsPerPage`/`currentPage`; `IResponse<T>` used `doc` nested under `data`\n- [x] **Fixed `common.interface.ts`**:\n  - `IListResponse<T>.data` changed from nested `{ docs: T[] }` to flat `T[]`\n  - `IResponse<T>.data` changed from `{ doc: T }` to flat `T`\n  - `IMeta` made `currentPage`, `page`, `itemsPerPage`, `limit` optional to handle both naming conventions\n- [x] **Fixed all module response interfaces** (changed `docs:` to `data:`):\n  - `coursesStudents.interface.ts` — `ICourseStudentFilterResponse`, `ICourseStudentLabelFilterResponse`\n  - `workCalendars.interface.ts` — `IWorkCalendarListResponse`\n  - `lessons.interface.ts` — `ILessonListResponse`\n  - `exams.interface.ts` — `IExamListResponse`, `IExamLinceceResponse`, `IExamFilterData`, `IExamGroupFilterData`\n  - `internalCosts.interface.ts` — `IInternalCostsResponse`\n  - `notifyConfigs.interface.ts` — `IListNotifyConfigsByFilter`\n  - `studentInfos.interface.ts` — `IStudentInfoResponse`\n  - `teacherInfos.interface.ts` — `IListTeacherRankings`\n  - `users.interface.ts` — `IUserResponse` (single-item response type)\n  - `courses.interface.ts` — `ICourseResponse` (single-item response type)\n- [x] **Fixed `GetTeacherRankingsUseCase.ts`**: Changed `IGetTeacherRankingsResponse.result` → `data`, mapped repository `docs` to `data` in execute()\n- [x] **Fixed `leadSources.service.ts`**: Added missing `totalPages` to meta object\n- [x] **Created stub JSON config files**:\n  - `src/config/permissions.json` — `[]`\n  - `src/config/routeDetailForPermissions.json` — `[]`\n- [x] **Fixed services returning `{ docs, meta }`** → `{ data, meta }`:\n  - `devices.service.ts`, `internalCosts.service.ts`, `lessons.service.ts`, `users.service.ts`, `courses.service.ts`, `exams.service.ts`, `studentInfos.service.ts`, `workCalendars.service.ts`, `notifyConfigs.service.ts`\n- [x] **Fixed controllers destructuring `{ docs: data, meta }`** → `{ data, meta }`:\n  - `studentInfos.controller.ts`, `exams.controller.ts`, `leadInfos.controller.ts`, `internalCostTypes.controller.ts`\n- [x] **Fixed `teacherLicenseCategories.controller.ts`**: Changed `result.docs` → `result.data`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **DTLX BE build fix** — Build still failing after ~25+ fixes. Remaining errors (as of last build):\n  - `studentInfos.controller.ts` — accesses `.docs` on `ILessonListResponse`, `IStudentInfosByFilterResponse`, `IStudentListFilterResponse`\n  - `teacherInfos.controller.ts` — accesses `.docs` on `ITeacherListFilterResponse`\n  - `teacherLicenseCategories.controller.ts` — `.data` does not exist on `ITeacherLicenseCategoriesListResponse`\n  - `users/sales.controller.ts` — accesses `.docs` on `ISaleListFilterResponse`\n  - `users/users.controller.ts` — accesses `.docs` on `ISaleListFilterResponse`\n  - `users/users.service.ts` — still returning `{ docs: IUserResponse[], meta }` (partially fixed multi-line)\n  - `workCalendars.service.ts` — still returning `{ docs: result, meta }` (partially fixed)\n  - `studentInfos.service.ts` — still returning `{ docs: docs.map(...)` (partially fixed)\n  - `courses.controller.ts`, `exams.controller.ts` — still accessing `.docs` on filter response types\n\n### Blocked\n- DTLX Backend cannot start until remaining TypeScript errors are resolved\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Interface-first fix approach**: Updated interfaces to match what services/controllers actually return, since services are the stable contract and clean-architecture migration partially updated interfaces but missed many files.\n- **Python regex over edit tool**: Used Python scripts for multi-line pattern replacement across 10+ files simultaneously rather than manual per-file edits.\n- **IMeta made flexible**: Made `currentPage`/`page` and `itemsPerPage`/`limit` optional rather than forcing one naming convention across all services.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Continue fixing DTLX BE build errors** — Build still failing, ~10+ remaining error groups:\n   - `users/users.service.ts` — fix remaining `return { docs: users.map(...)` pattern (multi-line, grep found it at line 226)\n   - `workCalendars.service.ts` — fix remaining `return { docs: result, meta: meta, }` pattern (multi-line)\n   - `studentInfos.service.ts` — fix remaining `return { docs: docs.map(...)` pattern (multi-line)\n   - All controllers accessing `.docs` on filter response types: need to change to `.data`\n   - `teacherLicenseCategories.interface.ts` — check `ITeacherLicenseCategoriesListResponse` interface (needs `data` instead of `docs`)\n   - `courses.controller.ts` lines 57, 80 — still access `.docs` on `ICoursesFilterResponse`\n   - `exams.controller.ts` lines 260, 285 — still access `.docs`\n   - `users/sales.controller.ts` lines 36, 59 — still access `.docs` on `ISaleListFilterResponse`\n   - `users/users.controller.ts` line 143 — still access `.docs`\n   - `studentInfos.controller.ts` — still destructures `{ docs: data, meta }`\n2. After build succeeds: start BE on port 5555\n3. Test APIs module-by-module: auth (public) → system → education → operation → notification (protected)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **QLHV BE MR !6**: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/merge_requests/6 — needs Lead approval/merge\n- **DTLX BE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend`, branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`, commit `47d53ae1`\n- **DTLX FE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend`, branch `main`, running on port 3000\n- **DTLX BE project ID**: 77055841, **FE project ID**: 77055851\n- **DTLX BE env**: `.env` (copied from `.env.example`), PORT=5555, MongoDB `mongodb://localhost:27017/dtlx`, Redis `localhost:6379/9`\n- **DTLX BE build command**: `yarn build` (fails) → `yarn dev` (nodemon `src/server.ts`)\n- **Backend processes currently running**: DTLX FE (`clear-mist`, port 3000)\n- **Remaining files with docs→data fix needed**: `src/modules/users/users.service.ts` (line 226), `src/modules/workCalendars/workCalendars.service.ts` (line 98), `src/modules/studentInfos/studentInfos.service.ts` (line 208), multiple controller files\n- **Build session**: `tender-wharf` — last build still running/polling\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nResume task from Lead: fix TypeScript errors in `ahv-dtlx-backend`, build successfully, start BE server, and test API module auth. User specified: \"Không cần spawn subagent TroLy model. Dùng AHV-Holding-DEV.\"\n\n## Early Progress\n- **TypeScript errors fixed**: Mass systematic fix of `docs` → `data` field mismatch across ~15+ interface files, ~10+ service files, and ~10+ controller files. Root cause: interfaces defined `data:` but services/controllers returned/accessed `docs:`. Fixed via Python regex scripts + manual sed commands.\n- **Build succeeded** after all fixes.\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe suffix continues from a failing `seed.ts` run. The seed script (`initBuiltInRoles`) iterates `BuiltInRoleSeeds` and calls `rolesService.getRoleByName()` for each, but the service **throws** on \"not found\" instead of returning null — causing the seed to fail before creating any roles. The error chain:\n\n```\ninitBuiltInRoles → getRoleByName(\"sale\") → throws \"Không tìm thấy thông tin vai trò này\" → seed fails\n```\n\nThe `sale` role was the last to be seeded (admin role was manually inserted via mongosh first). The BE server (PID 104391/104486) is confirmed running on port 5555 with MongoDB connected. The auth endpoint `/api/v1/auth/signin` responds correctly (rejects bad credentials). Only the seed process to create the `admin123@gmail.com` account remains incomplete.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/application/usecases/teachers/GetTeacherRankingsUseCase.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/helpers/env.helper.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/infrastructure/database.adapter.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/interfaces/common.interface.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/notifications/fcm/fcm.config.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/notifications/fcm/fcm.service.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/config/permissions.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/config/routeDetailForPermissions.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/notifyConfigs/notifyConfigs.interface.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/teacherInfos/teacherInfos.interface.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"0b4c1256","tokensBefore":101642,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/application/usecases/teachers/GetTeacherRankingsUseCase.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/helpers/env.helper.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/infrastructure/database.adapter.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/interfaces/common.interface.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/notifications/fcm/fcm.config.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/common/notifications/fcm/fcm.service.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/config/permissions.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/config/routeDetailForPermissions.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/notifyConfigs/notifyConfigs.interface.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/teacherInfos/teacherInfos.interface.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json"]},"fromHook":false}
