{"type":"message","id":"ff645229","parentId":"0a9d494d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:08:19.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, but the debug middleware I added to `index.js` logs BEFORE the auth middleware. So when the request comes in, it goes:\n1. `router.use((req, res, next) => { console.log(...); next(); })` → logs `[DEBUG index] request path= /system/roles`\n2. `router.use(authMiddleware.auth())` → passes, logs `[DEBUG auth] passport OK, calling next()`\n3. `router.use(system_route_1.default)` → should enter system.route.js\n\nBut `listenNotify` doesn't appear. The debug middleware I added to system.route.js should also appear. Let me restart and test again:","thinkingSignature":"4ef88cd5d7a163e0b92f04cf7a1a27ef20ae3d1fbe8af5d7423bdd9217cba76b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8oktt3qwqaj7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"kill $(ss -tlnp | grep 5555 | grep -oP 'pid=\\K[0-9]+') 2>/dev/null; sleep 2; bash /tmp/start-dtlx-debug.sh &\nsleep 10\necho \"=== TEST ===\"\nTOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:5555/api/v1/auth/signin -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"}' | python3 -c \"import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin)['data']['accessToken'])\")\ncurl -s -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" http://localhost:5555/api/v1/system/roles | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('status'))\"\necho \"=== LOG ===\"\ntail -10 /tmp/dtlx-be-debug.log | grep \"DEBUG\"","yieldMs":20000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":114,"output":367,"cacheRead":79795,"cacheWrite":557,"totalTokens":80833,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776139691630,"responseId":"062cf0adef9e5067ae453e24b39ddd60"}}
