{"type":"message","id":"b7b995ae","parentId":"d38f534a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:14:25.900Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"- GET `/api/v1/guests` ✅ 200\n- POST `/api/v1/guests` ❌ 400 (Validation failed - likely missing required fields)\n\nThe API is working correctly! The 400 for POST /guests is expected because the validation failed (missing required fields for guest registration).\n\nNow let me also fix the remaining issue: the correct paths for the API. The documentation in the original spec says `/api/v1/students` but it's actually `/api/v1/users/students`. Similarly for teachers.\n\nLet me now clean up the debug logging and do a proper summary. But first, let me test a few more important endpoints to make sure the API is working:","thinkingSignature":"147af6876d760efb963af627890b2971649d7390e5fe7dba311e71f9a53cb002"},{"type":"text","text":"API hoạt động! Giờ clean debug logs và test chính thức:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_45b09de0enk8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Restore original dist files (remove debug logs)\ncp /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/dist/presentation/api/v1/index.js.bak4 /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/dist/presentation/api/v1/index.js\necho \"Restored index.js\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":218,"output":266,"cacheRead":94771,"cacheWrite":1069,"totalTokens":96324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776140058285,"responseId":"062cf21bc331d49eb30b297aea932b0d"}}
